reviewText: I love Bob and Marge!  They say it like it should be...life in truth and honesty.  I can relate!  Funny, honest, innocent,and down to earth!  All series are great!

I majored in animation in school but fell initially fell in love with B&M while watching Comedy Central. Great show. I wish I had the money to get the newer seasons though.

Side note, the creators of the series are really nice and actually respond to emails!

Can't stress enough how enjoyable this series is,a wonderful creation and best animated series I've seen or could ever relate to. Great for the young,old,single or married,everyone can relate and have fun watching the adventures these two go through. Its a must buy!

More observational humour and I couldn't stop laughing! I am a die-hard  Bob and Margaret fan, so I jumped to buy this when realeased. Poking fun at  everything that small in life, you will feel like watching an animated  Seinfeld. I really wish the U.S. would give more attention to Bob and  Margaret.
